# Tmux Cheat Sheet - Drew's Configuration

# Session Management

# Cheat
# Type         bindkey
# Trigger      Ctrl+A d
# Domain       tmux
# Function     detach-client
# Executable   no
# Description  Detach from current session
# Short        Detach session

# Cheat
# Type         bindkey
# Trigger      Ctrl+A o
# Domain       tmux
# Function     sessionx plugin - session switcher
# Executable   no
# Description  Open interactive session switcher with zoxide integration
# Short        Session switcher

# Cheat
# Type         bindkey
# Trigger      Ctrl+A S
# Domain       tmux
# Function     choose-tree -s
# Executable   no
# Description  Choose session from tree view
# Short        Choose session

# Window Management

# Cheat
# Type         bindkey
# Trigger      Ctrl+A C-c
# Domain       tmux
# Function     new-window -c /Users/drew
# Executable   no
# Description  Create new window in home directory
# Short        New window (home)

# Cheat
# Type         bindkey
# Trigger      Ctrl+A n
# Domain       tmux
# Function     next-window
# Executable   no
# Description  Go to next window
# Short        Next window

# Cheat
# Type         bindkey
# Trigger      Ctrl+A C-n
# Domain       tmux
# Function     next-window
# Executable   no
# Description  Go to next window (alt binding)
# Short        Next window

